ink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg><span class="text-sm">Massachusetts, USA</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-500"><p>© PlausiDen LLC. All rights reserved.</p><div class="flex gap-6"><a href="/privacy-directive"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Privacy Directive</span></a><a href="/terms-of-service"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Terms of Service</span></a></div></div></div></footer></div></div></body></html>
